Package org.neo4j.internal.index.label

Class TokenScanLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.index.internal.gbptree.Layout.Adapter<TokenScanKey,​TokenScanValue>
      • org.neo4j.internal.index.label.TokenScanLayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparator<TokenScanKey>, Layout<TokenScanKey,​TokenScanValue>
    public class TokenScanLayout
extends Layout.Adapter<TokenScanKey,​TokenScanValue>
    Layout for GBPTree used by NativeTokenScanStore.
    • Each keys is a combination of tokenId and entityIdRange (entityId/64).
    • Each value is a 64-bit bit set (a primitive long) where each set bit in it represents a entity with that token, such that entityId = entityIdRange+bitOffset. Range size is 64 bits.
